#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:guest_house.product_template_11
msgid ""
"Free cancellation up to 48h prior your stay.<br>50% refund within the 48h."
msgstr "ຍົກເລີກຟຣີກ່ອນການເຂົ້າພັກ 48 ຊົ່ວໂມງ.<br>ຄືນເງິນ 50% ຫາກຍົກເລີກພາຍໃນ 48 ຊົ່ວໂມງ."

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"From the <strong>Guest House App</strong>, you can manage your bookings.<br/"
">The\n"
"            Guest House App relies on the Rental and Planning Apps binding, "
"with a few\n"
"            customizations."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດຈັດການການຈອງຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຈາກ <strong>ແອັບເຮືອນພັກ</strong>.<br/>ແອັບ\n"
"            ເຮືອນພັກນີ້ເຮັດວຽກຮ່ວມກັບແອັບການເຊົ່າ (Rental) ແລະ ການວາງແຜນ (Planning), "
"ໂດຍມີການ\n"
"            ປັບແຕ່ງບາງສ່ວນ."

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"From the Roles sections, you can select the companies and branches this "
"employee shall have access to as well as the default one."
msgstr ""
"ຈາກພາກສ່ວນບົດບາດ (Roles), ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກບໍລິສັດ ແລະ ສາຂາທີ່ພະນັກງານຜູ້ນີ້ສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງໄດ້ "
"ລວມທັງກຳນົດຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ."

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"From the search bar select the Today filter to see to check in and to check "
"out\n"
"                orders."
msgstr ""
"ຈາກແຖບຄົ້ນຫາ, ໃຫ້ເລືອກຕົວຕອງ \"ມື້ນີ້\" (Today) ເພື່ອເບິ່ງລາຍການແຈ້ງເຂົ້າ ແລະ ແຈ້ງອອກ\n"
